day4

create a simple python docker image  push the image to docker hub
step 1
docker login
docker build -t username/imagename:latest
docker push username/imagename:latest



step 2
how to create pod in k8s

command :  kubectl apply -f pod.yml

how to view created pod

command : kubectl get pods -o wide or kubectl get pods


delete the pod:

command: kubectl delete pods pod name